{
  "stem": "13251.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that doesn't qualify for Youth Aliyah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You have to be under 18.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You have to be under 18.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they refused to send him by himself because they didn't want to separate us because we were always together, or they didn't think it was a good idea.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was kind of pressured into making a decision.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] well, I guess partially for my brother's sake, you know, I, I made that decision.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they also said that they would-- you know, they have art schools in, in Israel and Jerusalem, Bezalel, which is a great art school.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there's a good chance that they would send me to art school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, that didn't happen, [LAUGHS] you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Ended up, we went to Israel, which is something, of course, I was always-- I always wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had a passion to go to Israel, just like I had a passion to, to do art.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was a difficult decision for me, but I made it, hoping I'll pick up on the art somehow later on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I tried.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I tried.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I, I took art courses in Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I took art courses wherever I could, but I missed a great opportunity.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I had the scholarship at a great school in London.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I remember the principal told me when-- you'll be sorry, he said to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because it was-- but I didn't have nobody else to advise me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I had no parents, nobody else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] You know, it's funny.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We never considered ourselves as orphans because there was always that hope that our parents were alive somewhere.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But basically, that's the way we grew up, like orphans, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, you know, there was no contact with parents after that.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
